title: Week 17 Recap: Who's going to the playoffs?!
itunes:title: Week 17 Recap: Who's going to the playoffs?!
description:
A room filled with heroes- Dan Hanzus, Marc Sessler, Gregg Rosenthal & Chris Wesseling- recap all of the action from the final week of the regular season, including Andy Dalton's late game heroics for the Bengals … and Bills (12:00); Buffalo finally has its moment as the Bills are headed to the postseason (19:30); The end of a sad, sad season for the winless Browns (35:00); A crazy game call in the Cheifs' win over the Broncos (44:30); An in-studio New Year's Eve toast (1:10:00) and much more!

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
